public class ExternalJob
extends ViewJob<ExternalJob,ExternalRun>

Job that runs outside Hudson whose result is submitted to Hudson (either via web interface, or simply by placing files on the file system, for compatibility.)

Author:
Kohsuke Kawaguchi

reload

Description copied from class: ViewJob
Reloads the list of Runs. This operation can take a long time.

The loaded Runs should be set to ViewJob.runs.
